headline: 4 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: Try not to let market volatility bring you down. Instead, let dividend stocks make you happy. These high-yield dividend stocks will pay you between 3% and 7% to hold them.

headline: Is PepsiCo Stock a Buy, Sell, or Hold in 2025?
summary: Like an open can of soda left out overnight, PepsiCo (NASDAQ: PEP) stock has lost its fizz lately -- it's down by about 15% over the past year at the time of this writing.  Does the stock's current weakness point to more downside ahead, or are there good reasons for investors to stay optimistic?  A reality of investing is that even the best companies sometimes get caught up in stock market volatility.
